title: UFO Factory
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Corktown bar and music venue offers food, under the name "Laika Dog," consisting of customizeable vegan hot dogs as well vegan grilled cheese, tater tots and fries. Choose from toppings like vegan cheese and chili, fried ramen, and kim chi. Music ranges from electronic to rock. Art exhibitions from local artists rotate. Bar is open until 2am.
